<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>About</title>

    <style>
        .content {
            max-width: 980px;
            margin: 40px auto 70px;
            padding: 0 18px;
        }

        .card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            padding: 28px;
            border-radius: var(--radius);
            border: 1px solid var(--line);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
        }

        h1 {
            margin: 0 0 12px;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-family: "Fraunces", serif;
        }

        p {
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0 0 12px;
            color: var(--muted);
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <%- include("partials/navbar") %>

    <!-- About Content -->
    <div class="content">
        <div class="card">
            <h1>About E-Learning</h1>

            <p>
                Welcome to our E-Learning platform! This project is designed to help students 
                learn anytime, anywhere with ease and flexibility.
            </p>

            <p>
                This platform provides a simple and user-friendly interface where users can 
                register, login, and access learning resources efficiently.
            </p>

            <p>
                Our goal is to make education more accessible and interactive using modern 
                web technologies.
            </p>

            <p>
                This project is developed as a full-stack application using Node.js, Express, 
                MongoDB, and EJS.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <%- include("partials/footer") %>

</body>
</html>
